#, no-c-format
msgid "Storage Devices"
msgstr "Naprave za shranjevanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The module window displays the available file devices and some information "
"about each device. It also allows you to control mount points, and mount/"
"unmount devices."
msgstr ""
"Ta modul prikazuje datotečne naprave, ki so na voljo, ter nekatere "
"informacije o vsaki napravi. Omogoča vam tudi nadzor nad priklopnimi točkami "
"in priklopljenimi/odklopljenimi napravami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normally, the following pieces of information are shown in this tab:"
msgstr "Ponavadi so prikazane naslednje informacije v tem zavihku:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "an icon depicting the type of storage"
msgstr "ikona, ki prikazuje tip shranitvenega prostora"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "device name"
msgstr "ime naprave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "file system type"
msgstr "vrsta datotečnega sistema"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "total size"
msgstr "celotna velikost"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "mount point"
msgstr "priklopna točka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "free disk space"
msgstr "nezaseden prostor diska"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "the percentage of space used as a number and as a graph."
msgstr "procent uporabljenega prostora v obliki številke in grafa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> clicking on the header of a particular "
"column sorts the devices according to that variable. A second "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click sorts in the opposite order."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Levi</mousebutton> klik na glavo določenegastolpca, bo "
"razvrstil naprave v zvezi s tistim kriterijem. Drugi<mousebutton>levi</"
"mousebutton> klik razporedi po obratnem vrstnem redu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> clicking on a row pops up a menu. If that "
"device is not currently mounted, the <guimenuitem>Mount Device</guimenuitem> "
"option is available. If the device is mounted, it can be unmounted by "
"choosing <guimenuitem>Unmount Device</guimenuitem>. Selecting "
"<guimenuitem>Open in File Manager</guimenuitem> opens a new window with a "
"graphical view of the files on that device."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Desni</mousebutton> klik na vrstico odpre meni. Če ta naprava "
"trenutno ni priklopljena, je na voljo možnost <guimenuitem>Priklopi napravo</"
"guimenuitem>. Če je naprava nameščena, jo lahko odstranite z izbiro "
"<guimenuitem>Odklopi napravo</guimenuitem>. Z izbiro možnosti "
"<guimenuitem>Odpri v upravljalniku datotek </guimenuitem> se odpre novo okno "
"z grafičnim prikazom datotek v tej napravi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The appropriate mount and unmount commands, and how the file manager is "
"opened from the context menu, can be configured from the &kdiskfree; "
"application."
msgstr ""
"Ustrezne ukaze za priklop in odklop ter način odpiranja upravitelja datotek "
"iz kontekstnega menija lahko nastavite v aplikaciji &kdiskfree;."

